videos.title: Esper Dragons IS SO BACK
videos.description:
Dragonlords Ojutai & Silumgar are back for the first time on Arena. You know we had to play one of our favorite All-Star decks again. We even got Jace and Ojutai's Command!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some MTG cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish

► Read more about this deck (full article): https://www.mtggoldfish.com/articles/single-scoop-esper-dragons-is-so-back
